From dea9192fa110aedf2fab14ae905e45f32e9c170b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: searoisme <haipeng.jiang@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 1 Apr 2026 14:59:10 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] riscv: evl: fix build errors for SpacemiT K1 EVL port

Fix all build errors encountered when building the EVL-enabled kernel
for SpacemiT K1 (RISC-V64, Milk-V Jupiter board).

Changes:
- arch/riscv/include/asm/syscall.h: add syscall_get_arg0() returning
  regs->orig_a0, required by linux/dovetail.h for OOB syscall detection

- arch/riscv/include/asm/thread_info.h: move dovetail/thread_info.h
  include inside #ifndef __ASSEMBLY__ block to prevent assembly errors

- arch/riscv/include/asm/evl/calibration.h: new file, RISC-V clock
  gravity default (3000 ns)

- arch/riscv/include/asm/evl/fptest.h: new file, RISC-V FPU test hooks
  using CONFIG_FPU guard

- arch/riscv/include/uapi/asm/evl/fptest.h: new file, RISC-V FPU test
  macros using fmv.d.x / fmv.x.d instructions (D-extension)

- arch/riscv/kernel/irq_pipeline.c: new file, RISC-V arch hooks for
  Dovetail IRQ pipeline (arch_do_IRQ_pipelined, arch_irq_pipeline_init)

- arch/riscv/kernel/smp.c: add irq_send_oob_ipi() using
  __ipi_send_mask(ipi_desc[slot], cpumask) for OOB IPI dispatch

- arch/riscv/kernel/Makefile: add irq_pipeline.o under CONFIG_IRQ_PIPELINE

- include/asm-generic/evl/thread_info.h: add #ifndef __ASSEMBLY__ guard
  to prevent C struct definitions from being seen by assembler

- include/dovetail/mm_info.h: include asm-generic/evl/mm_info.h when
  CONFIG_EVL is set (provides EVL_MM_PTSYNC_BIT and oob_mm_state)

- include/dovetail/poll.h: include asm-generic/evl/poll.h when
  CONFIG_EVL is set (provides EVL_POLL_NR_CONNECTORS, evl_poll_connector)

- include/dovetail/thread_info.h: include asm-generic/evl/thread_info.h
  when CONFIG_EVL is set (provides full oob_thread_state)

- include/evl/thread.h: add #include <evl/wait.h> before
  evl_put_thread_wchan() to provide full struct evl_wait_channel definition

- include/linux/mmc/host.h: restore SpacemiT-specific encrypt_config
  callback and MMC_CAP2_DISABLE_PROBE_SCAN capability that were lost
  when EVL headers were bulk-copied

- fs/ioctl.c: add compat_ptr_oob_ioctl() for EVL compat ioctl support

Signed-off-by: SpacemiT K1 EVL Port <evl@spacemit.com>
